{"word":"Barrenness","slug":"barrenness","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Barrenness</b> Sterility of women.<br/> A reproach<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=30&verse=23'>Gen 30:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=7'>1Sa 1:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=11'>1Sa 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=4&verse=1'>Isa 4:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=25'>Luk 1:25</a><br/> Miraculously removed, instances of:<br/> - Sarai<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=21'>Gen 17:21</a> <br/> - Rebecca<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=21'>Gen 25:21</a> <br/> - Manoah's wife<br/> <a href='B:'></a> <br/> - Hannah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=20'>1Sa 1:20</a> <br/> - Elizabeth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=25'>Luk 1:25</a> <br/> Sent as a judgment<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=20&verse=18'>Gen 20:18</a><br/><a href='S:Childlessness'>Childlessness</a>"}]}